entries.femaleVariant: Have you ever heard of Jotaro Shobo? He's one of the T-Claws.
What's got you all glum?
You hear about Riko Jinsey?
Second floor is for VIP customers only.
As establishments fucked sideways go, this one takes the whole damn pie.
Hear that?
Yeah, I've heard. A fuckin' psycho. Likes to hurt people.
Not anymore. Apparently he died.
He finally pop a bullet in his brain after seein' himself in the mirror?
If only... No, I heard the Mox had him on their blacklist.
Some girls marked him for death.
Have you ever heard of Jotaro Shobo? He's one of the T-Claws.
Yeah, I've heard. A fuckin' psycho. Likes to hurt people.
The Mox have him on their blacklist. Some girls marked him for death.
Well that's all pudding, honey, but so what? Assholes like Shobo've been on MY blacklist before I heard of 'em.
The Mox blacklist is more powerful. It actually means something.
I'll believe it when I see his rotting, stinking corpse.
Amen to that.
I saw Mr. J today.
Thought you liked him. Thought he was your beau.
He is... but he didn't come to see me.
No. Is she related to that politician-or-whatever, that Natsuko?
Mh. Riko was her daughter. Found her dead.
Oooh. What happened?
Yoshi Wakinoto happened, that's what. Murdered her.
And he would be...?
Her input. You spend ANY time in realspace?
A T-Claw. Saw 'em here once, came in together. Chrome like that I've never seen, on anyone.
Could tell by the way he looked at her, he was butter in her hands…
So why did he kill her?
The one question I don't have an answer for…
Told you, that's how it is with this crowd. You can't get too close. Trust me – the more you treat 'em like shit, the more they'll come back.
What will you have?
Got a house special?
Got a house special, I'll take it.
You really think they remember nothing?
Anything. Whatever stands to fuck me up the quickest.
What do you mean, exactly?
Hard day?
More like hard life.
That's the whole point. They're not supposed to remember, not a smidge.
So why, every time, do they restart the conversation where we left off? That's not remembering?
It's saved to the doll-chips that store their personas.
Hold on, reel back a sec... You talk to them? Like, talk-talk?
Top-shelf. Lookin' to put the edge on, not take it off.
It depends what you like.
Go with your gut. Surprise me.
I can't get in? What's that mean? I'm here every motherfuckin' week!
You're not authorized to access the VIP area.
You can take it up with the manager.
Oh yes, I am.
Is there a problem?
No shortage of wise-asses.
This gonk don't understand that I've got a right to be in there.
From what I can see, your VIP membership has been revoked.
Please stay calm, sir. Or we gonna have to escort you outside.
I'll say. You going back upstairs?
In a minute. Need to piss, first.
Hold it there, honey. You seem to be in the wrong place.
Did you not hear? You need to leave.
Hey, no peeking! Bad luck, seein' us like this.
The fuck am I lookin' at?
Is this some kind of joke?
Not bad. But it would be much better real. I would eat those thighs.
At least I would hear no laments about pain. It hurts, it hurts.
What's going on?
What do you mean, real? She's all ones and zeroes.
Do you mean I can ask her to do anything? Literally anything?
It's a ho-lo-gram. What's so hard to get?
Your fuckin' holo's fuckin' with us!
Is that so? The hologram...?
This is unacceptable.
Please, sir, calm down.
Yeah, just stand there. That will fix it.
Would've had more choices if I didn't have a certain brain parasite.
Guess that makes you a real deviant.
May I see your credentials?
I'm calling security.
No, sir, you're not.
No, dawg, I'm takin' it up with you, here , now. You got any idea who I am?
Say what, now?
Ask? It's not about askin', man. Just gotta be programmed.
Let me have my fantasies!
Not like you know how to hack it, so why don't we just shut up and enjoy the show?
That's what I said.
Things always this quiet?
This place always this dead? Thought I heard a tumbleweed roll by.
Dead for you. Lively for others. For me, just right.
What can I get you?
I'll have another of the same.
Another of the same.
Get outta here!
'Cause of you.
